label: genericName
comment: The chemical/generic name of the fertilizer corresponding to this observation.

label: productName
comment: Name of the product corresponding to this observation.

label: productCode
comment: The unique code assigned to the product corresponding to this observation.

label: chemicalComposition
comment: The ordered array comprising the chemical/ organic composition of the fertilizer added to the soil

label: chemicalProportion
comment: The ordered array comprising the quantity/ measure of each compound contained in the fertilizer added to the soil.

label: certificateInfo
comment: Date of issual, expiry/validity, renewal of the document/certificate corresponding to this observation.

label: modelInfo
comment: Describes the model information of the device/sensor or system or product in consideration.

label: personnelInfo
comment: Personnel information of an individual or business corresponding to this observation.

label: manufacturerInfo
comment: Details of the manufacturer of the product/merchandise corresponding to this observation

label: mfgDate
comment: The date of manufature of the commodity or product corresponding to this observation.

label: maxResidueLimit
comment: The maximum concentration of the chemical or pesiticides permitted by the competent regulatory authority corresponding to this observation.

label: purposeDescription
comment: Descibes the purpose of the entity or service corresponding this observation.

label: storageGuidance
comment: The advice, direction, support, or recommendations for storing the goods, products and commodities in a storage plant.

label: precautionaryMeasures
comment: The action of being careful, vigilant, and the steps to avoid potential dangers or risks.

label: productExpiryDate
comment: Date of expiry of the product corresponding to this observation

label: subsidyAmount
comment: The amount of government subsidy for a product corresponding to this observation for the welfare of the people.
